+/**
+ * Build an Embeddings client for providers that expose embeddings APIs.
+ * Returns null for providers without native embeddings (Anthropic,
+ * OpenRouter, MiniMax, GLM) — the caller is expected to fall back to
+ * a non-embedding signal (e.g. lexical similarity).
